e (a list of\n    two-element lists) that pairs each operation name with a \n    JavaScript function\n    that implements the operation (that is, produces the same output value\n    given the same input values). The last argument specifies the controller\n    as a list of labels and machine instructions, as in\n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"5.1","href":"/sicpjs/5.1"},{"body":".\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    To compute GCDs with this machine, we set the input registers, start the\n    machine, and examine the result when the simulation terminates:\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":473,"program":"chap=4&-KC8LJT8rR1dMmZEKqESgAdxou36g1AAFpoUsVvQOmV6PYns8dAAuUApdJ8UhCchlPj3FT5TzeEpQirVWpMMpCdr0In0xllTgyFlM5zKEbHcZDUjTWYLeGrdacsrc6SgCWHNFsRIGM6cC6EK43SR3WaPdGvd4sT78CVS-6Xa63GUMpkwuHLTiI9rI1G645Y-GE4na9xFHylUDCKr0eqNATkChTIP0AAedWufGjwRkRnEkg5VrZvJ05FwoEyKv53CEhGYCfjMdJGjRfImguIIoL+OLTATTHu+FMCbJLoVpz4anmAD5QMQjjoPO82fQzjm83T082Y2XghXNC6G2cBZwRdSanUJXxZWnWQu9+ml6TR+ie0q+wsh1lOJfChP7dPc+drNxeCfz5n0euWBFSxWHYGxeEEEQU2lT9bBPEDaF-J9jmvGhb0HOhGCYfkeGLThHHyUA0XHJlX1XXUPi+JdTUIIFQRoBM2BWGIAhCKdYVFB0nS7MdyWKXxmIDIMIX2ag4LjBMk0gkwjxIno+hEoY-2HGsdmCbdKl3YMmj4YTBjg3pzzkvZBjlasBSWHwt0WYRgnjO9-SEQMtNDcNIxjZtcHjSTjFTS1WWGKQqxdYLdJifT5LVPDO247QUNzfshyEYJgjKQImAkVUrhYVKJHkAArIQZk4YhGmCUg+CC4L0V6STbJzdDPJUGQhEsi9eN9KE7XIWhCEcUCvxYE1QFWfRiFUStkL0JUyhscwup6swZBg79FGUGQRpYMayS8DrmPmwh4KlPh9vSgUckGJS4pxDJ3SJE6snOmI2p2yk9qYnrW1mdsf3us6ogujRCMmxVklSG6CSJW7jveg6Hv+p7nopfj-EEpgTrjLJvKgmS2SMyEDhkYJiCU9d8RYSwgMw5b+GTaTRW6g6nFWsIBTaszJjbNy1MWE7OZ-LIYuU8y+Z8BZKuVJhQtE0s+c7cW3lRqWDpbONZZjLG6cPVTjIOHVdSxVGGiaMNyAjMTPLVxMHJ86VZUFuK0KHMiqp0e1mGw+hcLxIRycYGQRaIPtBZd9IZhIIMib4ImCPFsdvSRv1Q6LMb6nWaOJtdzCPa9omZCh4Ds9IPDo4vQifVelHHKDHhuA8zIBQ13ytaV9lQFwelaEJ4mM+0dd+TSE3-EWGv3eoAfBnr7hBezd8VSVn9+8H2IlPZ2sx6XphResqvJfkvSVc82OXeP3v18GRvpSPk+XebvfdaQnQHYSnvr+0N2sOoHCi74duhE7oXx5hR8EHB+J8k7h1TlHYmBQr7H